title: Hoops Tonight - Warriors finish Grizzlies, Celtics force Game 7
itunes:title: Hoops Tonight - Warriors finish Grizzlies, Celtics force Game 7
description:
Jason breaks down a wild night of basketball, diving into how the Warriors pulled off a Game 6 win and looking at Tatum and the Celtics’ huge performance to stay alive against dominant Giannis and the Bucks. #Herd
